article_title: Clinicas de Salud del Pueblo clinic in Brawley soon to expand
article_text: An additional 5,000 patients a year are expected to be served at the Brawley Medical Clinic now that the facility is about to expand, according to an official with Clinicas de Salud del Pueblo.
